{
  "a_galaxy_workflow": "true",
  "annotation": "Phase C, chaining half (split out of the former combined align_chain_project; the gene-projection half is now WF-C2 project_annotations). Whole-genome alignment -&gt; reciprocal-best UCSC chains, as a SINGLE map-over with native Galaxy collection operations (no custom helpers). CROSS_PRODUCT_FLAT enumerates ordered strain pairs as two aligned target/query lists (the paired-slot -&gt; two-input binding gxformat2 could not express), FILTER_FROM_FILE drops self-pairs, the cleaned + rbest UCSC chain pipeline maps over them, and RELABEL_FROM_FILE rewrites A_B-&gt;A.B for Phase E. Proven bit-identical to per-pair driving on the Pv4 test panel.",
  "comments": [],
  "creator": [
    {
      "class": "Person",
      "identifier": "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5987-8032",
      "name": "Anton Nekrutenko"
    },
